                     <interp inst="t18200112-58-punish331" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="whipping"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200112-58-defend624 t18200112-58-punish331"></join>
               Whipped
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>London Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
